# Real Project Usage

### Logging

```java
employees.forEach(logger::info);
```

Instead of

```java
employees.forEach(e -> logger.info(e));
```

---

### Printing Data

```java
list.forEach(System.out::println);
```

---

### Entity Mapping

```java
employees.stream()
         .map(EmployeeDto::new)
         .toList();
```

If `EmployeeDto` has a constructor that accepts an `Employee`, each stream element is passed into that constructor.

---

### Convert to Uppercase

```java
names.stream()
     .map(String::toUpperCase)
     .toList();
```

---

### Sorting

```java
names.sort(String::compareToIgnoreCase);
```

