### Problem 2: Convert to uppercase

Using a lambda:

```java
List<String> names = Arrays.asList("java", "spring", "boot");
List<String> result = names.stream()
                           .map(s -> s.toUpperCase())
                           .toList();
```

Rewrite it using a method reference.

---

### Problem 3: Sort a list

Using a lambda:

```java
List<String> names = Arrays.asList("Dog", "Apple", "Cat");
names.sort((a, b) -> a.compareTo(b));
```

Rewrite it using a method reference.

